ChildCareTech.common

Enum SocketRequestType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SocketRequestType>
      • ChildCareTech.common.SocketRequestType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<SocketRequestType>

    public enum SocketRequestType
extends java.lang.Enum<SocketRequestType>
    The type of a socket request. One can assume that for each method in the UserSessionFacade interface there is a corresponding entry in this enum. The vice versa is true except for the LOGIN and REGISTER entries that correspond to methods in the UserSessionFactory interface.
